<template><div><PageHeader eyebrow="ADMIN / COMMENTS" title="评论审核" description="审核待发布评论并进行置顶、精华或删除操作"><el-button @click="load">刷新</el-button></PageHeader><el-table v-loading="loading" :data="rows" stripe><el-table-column prop="id" label="ID" min-width="170"/><el-table-column prop="userId" label="用户 ID" min-width="170"/><el-table-column prop="workId" label="作品 ID" min-width="170"/><el-table-column prop="content" label="评论内容" min-width="300"/><el-table-column prop="createdAt" label="提交时间" min-width="180"/><el-table-column label="操作" width="260"><template #default="{row}"><el-button size="small" type="success" @click="status(row,'APPROVED')">通过</el-button><el-button size="small" type="warning" @click="status(row,'REJECTED')">驳回</el-button><el-button size="small" type="danger" @click="remove(row)">删除</el-button></template></el-table-column></el-table><EmptyState v-if="!loading&&!rows.length" description="当前没有待审核评论"/></div></template>
<script setup>import { onMounted,ref } from 'vue';import PageHeader from '../../components/PageHeader.vue';import EmptyState from '../../components/EmptyState.vue';import { commentApi } from '../../api/comment';const loading=ref(false),rows=ref([]);async function load(){loading.value=true;try{rows.value=await commentApi.pending()}finally{loading.value=false}}async function status(row,value){await commentApi.setStatus(row.id,value);load()}async function remove(row){await commentApi.adminRemove(row.id);load()}onMounted(load)</script>
